      • getStartCron

        public CronExpression getStartCron()
        Get a CronExpression that triggers at each period opening. e.g. if the period is 9am-18pm, the result will be 0 9 * * *
        Returns:
        null if the period is always open, else the cron expression

      • getEndCron

        Returns:
